Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.39,0:00:02.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,上一集的Love Live! Superstar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:06.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Liella!再次出席學園偶像祭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:07.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而且這次還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:08.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,壓軸!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:11.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可可等人作為Love Live優勝候補前來參加
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:13.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,結果卻輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:16.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既然妳們都能當優勝候補
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:19.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看來這大賽也沒什麼大不了的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:21.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們永遠以妳們為傲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:24.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希望妳們今後也繼續以優勝為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:25.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,受到大家的鼓勵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:27.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Liella!又更加成長了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:29.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,朝著Love Live優勝前進吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:35.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好可愛…好可愛…!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.34,0:00:36.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學園偶像?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:38.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看著她們唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,總覺得我也感動了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:41.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要不要去試試看?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:44.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她們好像還在招募社員
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:45.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要不要考慮看看呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:46.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:49.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我馬上去拿入社申請表來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:51.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不 我不是那個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.91,0:00:56.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我太吵了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:01:00.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不小心又在米女同學面前提到學園偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.12,0:01:03.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我不是說我沒興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:10.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來 奮戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:14.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,掀起我們的旋風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:16.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爬上巔峰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:17.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們絕不認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.89,0:01:19.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要拿下勝利!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:29.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不夠 還不夠 遠遠不夠!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:32.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不論何時我都要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:35.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超越昨天的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:38.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,究竟能走到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.12,0:01:39.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然仍舊不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:40.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還是要燃燒自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:43.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想與你一同歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:46.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想了解尚未知曉的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:49.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我還會更加成長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:51.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不想輕易放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:55.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:57.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在立刻 Start up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:00.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,向頂點前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:03.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還要更加 更進一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:06.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,更加情緒高昂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:09.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去實現吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:11.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在這瞬間 盡自己所能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:14.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,追尋夢想 盡自己全力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:19.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為邂逅 給了我熱情的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:22.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:26.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算是不可能的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:27.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也去實現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:30.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們會繼續相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:33.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯 WE WILL!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:39.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(#04 科學教室的兩人)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:40.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,社長?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:41.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:43.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,社團數量也越來越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:46.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想下次應該可以來舉辦社長會議
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:50.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說起來我們都還沒決定誰當社長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:55.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,盯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:57.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,盯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:01.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,決定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:03.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等等 先等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:05.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要來投票嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,贊成小香音當社長的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:07.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:10.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希奈子從入社以來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:12.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就一直覺得香音學姐是社長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:14.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,當然會這樣覺得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:16.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可可也覺得香音比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:17.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,決定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:19.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別這麼乾脆就下結論啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:20.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳這麼不想當嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:23.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,與其說不想…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希奈子也贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:27.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢竟戀學姐還有學生會的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:30.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,剩下的學姐就很少能當社長的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:33.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳是不是順口就說了很傷人的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:35.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:39.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,總之看來各位已經有共識了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:48.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她們在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:49.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:50.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:54.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既然社長選好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:55.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就從昨天的舞步繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:56.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,社長?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:57.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她們在選社長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:58.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最後選了誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:03:59.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然是澀谷學姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,難道是平安名學姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:02.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還是舞蹈核心嵐學姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:04.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不 也有可能是可可學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:06.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,戀學姐還有學生會可能有點難…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說這又是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:10.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,收訊不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,才不是咧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:14.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是問妳什麼時候搞了這種東西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:15.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:19.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只是實驗用的收音麥克風剛好放在屋頂上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:20.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不想聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:24.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能想聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那妳為什麼每天都在看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:30.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳看嘛 我在這又沒什麼事能做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:32.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,殺殺時間罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是嗎 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看得超專心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:40.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哭爆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:42.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳沒事幹嘛偷拍我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很可愛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,才不是可不可愛的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,正在看演唱會的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:48.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是世界上最不想被別人看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這可是全世界共通的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:54.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,總之這一切都只是剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她們剛好在練習 我就看看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:00.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳的臉…很紅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:02.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:03.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,繼續放任時間流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就要錯過加入的時機了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:07.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳真的無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:11.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,反正我又不想加入
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:14.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再說要是我不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:16.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,本來就有點陰暗的這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就會變得更加陰暗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:21.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(科學愛好會 臨時社辦)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:26.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:29.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,完美的圓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:30.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小香音 快…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:32.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小香音?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:39.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳還是不太想當社長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:42.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也不是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:46.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學園偶像可是小香音最先開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:47.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不對喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:49.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是小可可開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:53.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過 將大家凝聚在一起的是小香音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:55.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,或許是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但正因如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.17,0:05:58.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我認為如果要Liella!蛻變的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:01.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,應該讓其他人當社長更好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:04.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,例如…小千之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:06.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我? 我不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:07.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:10.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為…我不適合這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:17.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個…我有點事想談談
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:24.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小希奈子今天也要去社團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:28.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有興趣的話隨時都歡迎參觀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:30.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們在屋頂等妳喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:35.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我又在教室提到學園偶像了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:39.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對不起 真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:40.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我又沒生…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是的 已經走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:53.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,四季 妳也試著跟同學混熟一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:54.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,繼續這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:56.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,又要跟國中那時一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,幹嘛 妳在生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:02.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,春假時妳不是說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:05.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,上高中後要稍微努力看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:10.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳有在聽我說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,受不了 搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:39.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就請先自我介紹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:40.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是若菜四季
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:43.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小四季好像是看了之前的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,開始對學園偶像產生興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:47.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:50.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天就先來體驗學園偶像看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:52.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是一年級耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:55.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟希奈子一樣是一年級的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:57.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在是怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳怎麼會站在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:02.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:07.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好 不錯喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:16.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看來妳的身體跟可可差不多柔軟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:18.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,意外地輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天都難得來一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:24.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就來體驗一下簡單的舞步跟隊形吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:29.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟大家一起跳舞真的很開心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:35.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳先過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:38.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:40.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:44.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:48.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好了 要開始囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:49.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:55.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,四季跟她們站在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:58.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:03.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:05.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼有種既視感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:08.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是 那個 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:10.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她叫芽衣 一年級的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:12.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:17.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳該不會也對學園偶像有興趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:19.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒 沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:20.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她一直在那邊看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:24.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,意思是妳很有興趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:27.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不嫌棄的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:30.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要不要體驗一下學園偶像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:34.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我嗎? 學園偶像?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:38.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:49.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,四季妳又想怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:52.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的想當學園偶像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:56.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我還沒決定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:00.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,少騙人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:06.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣 好不容易都…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就說我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:12.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小芽衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:21.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:24.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:26.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這裡是?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:29.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,二樓角落的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 那裡有什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:34.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,從這邊看不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:35.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:37.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,貼在那邊的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:44.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是Liella!的海報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:46.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下面是三年前限量販售的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:48.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,歷代學園偶像大全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:50.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那旁邊還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,櫃子上好像也有什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:01.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(傳說的偶像傳說 DVD-Box)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:02.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可可學姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:05.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,傳說中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:08.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,傳傳傳…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:10.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哭什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:11.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:13.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我可是第一次親眼看見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是那片傳說中的DVD耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:17.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這可是在二手網站永遠能拍出天價
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:19.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-在學園偶像… -夠了夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那到底是誰的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:22.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:26.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小芽衣…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:27.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,快躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,總覺得好像有人在看這邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:47.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:58.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,錯覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:04.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,芽衣的視力不怎麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:07.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:09.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她常常瞪別人也是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:11.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她視力不好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:13.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然我早就叫她戴眼鏡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:18.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,結果讓班上同學都有點怕她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:20.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明明只要說清楚就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為她不太會說話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:27.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小四季跟小芽衣從以前就是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:28.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:31.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:33.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我不確定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:42.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們第一次認識是在國中的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:45.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,本來我總是自己一人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:48.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也非常習慣這種生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:53.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小芽衣 要走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:55.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:58.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一開始她只是普通地來搭話而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:12:59.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:02.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:09.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們之間本應到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:10.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:14.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳真的很囉嗦耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就說我不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:21.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(烏龜的飼養方法)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,打擾到妳了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:23.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:28.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,打擾的人是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:37.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要跟誰做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,或是不跟誰做朋友之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:44.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼群體行動總是會變得那麼麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:48.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:52.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也跟妳一樣比較喜歡獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我本以為那只是玩笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:59.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是我跟芽衣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:02.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,從那之後就每天都在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:04.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(科學社)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:07.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,知道我想創立科學社的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:10.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她明明沒興趣卻還是加入了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:18.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明明她其實比較喜歡學園偶像?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:20.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,芽衣會來讀這所學校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:23.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是因為想試著當看看學園偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:24.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為這裡有Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:27.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是她卻遲遲無法踏出那一步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小四季妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:33.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,會來體驗加入學園偶像社
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:35.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就只是為了小芽衣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:39.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:41.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:42.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:46.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想小芽衣一定是無法拋下小四季一人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:48.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:51.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為科學社就只有妳們兩個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:53.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,完全無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:56.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我明明都沒為芽衣做過任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:58.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(登日搬家公司)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:00.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,腰…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:04.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,夏美的腰…要鬼夏了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:07.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,回家後還得拍攝跟剪輯影片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:09.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,忙死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:12.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,先躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:16.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳還真晚來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:18.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是跑哪去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:20.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:23.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是要問妳到底想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:26.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳還是坦率點比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:29.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學園偶像社裡都是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:30.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我又不是在說我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:32.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是在說妳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:35.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我喜歡獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:38.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也從來沒拜託妳陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:39.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為這裡是新學校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:42.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,科學社就算只有一個社員也不會廢社
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:44.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不必擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:46.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,快點去學園偶像社吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以我不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:50.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我不適合當學園偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:52.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那妳也別再來科學教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:55.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明明沒興趣卻一直待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:57.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,反而讓我很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:03.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:06.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不適合…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:13.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:15.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小千什麼事都辦得到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我辦不到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:27.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小千只是以為自己辦不到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:28.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:30.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小香音…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:38.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,總之既然她對學園偶像這麼了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:40.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她肯定是個黃金級新人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:41.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想點辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:42.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別那麼煩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:44.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我才沒有煩人家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:47.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不太順利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:48.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不適合…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小芽衣她已經這麼想了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:58.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明明或許她只要改變想法就能做到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:03.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小香音 我跟妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:07.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(結丘女子高中 第一屆 社長會議)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:08.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:11.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,進行結丘女子高級中學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:13.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,第一屆社長會議
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:18.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是科學愛好會社長若菜四季
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:31.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是學園偶像社社長嵐千砂都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:35.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小千!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:36.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,千砂都同學居然!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:38.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要當社長!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:40.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然可能會給大家造成困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:44.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是我想挑戰看看自己能不能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:47.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我會追隨妳的 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:51.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:02.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小芽衣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:04.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,幹嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:05.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果要問學園偶像的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:07.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我可不打算加入
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:08.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:10.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這還用問
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:12.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我外表嚇人 個性又差
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不管怎麼想都不適合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:17.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明明還沒有試過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:18.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不能說自己不適合喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:19.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小芽衣之所以會猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:25.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是因為小四季對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:27.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳想跟她在一起對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:29.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:33.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再說 她說了自己更喜歡獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:36.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還說我很礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:38.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那都是騙妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:40.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小芽衣妳肯定也發覺了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:42.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢竟妳們兩個很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我跟四季很像?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:47.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了 完全不一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:57.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們都很容易害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:59.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很容易感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:01.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,討厭著這樣的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:04.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,逐漸屈就於現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:08.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,騙自己說是自己想這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:12.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想小四季一定也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:16.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我在屋頂看著妳們時就發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:18.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟小芽衣一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:20.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小四季也喜歡小芽衣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:25.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以小四季她肯定也喜歡學園偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學園偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:55.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:59.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒想到妳也會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:01.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我並不是特別喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:04.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只是因為妳好像有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:06.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,才查了點資料而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:13.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳的臉很紅喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:17.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,像我這種笑容都擺不好的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:20.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是無法當學園偶像的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:23.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳都這麼說了 我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:24.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:25.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為芽衣很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳比較可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:28.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,才不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:32.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:35.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:41.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,難得我們兩個相似的人相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:44.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要不要試著坦率一點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:50.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有四季在身邊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:53.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我就覺得應該能好好努力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:17.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天開始有兩位新人加入
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:21.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請 請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:24.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看來妳們在練習舞步前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:26.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要先練習露出笑容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:27.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真拿妳們沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:29.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我就來示範一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:30.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-Galaxy… -不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:33.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,至少讓我做完嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:34.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,社長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:37.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既然社員增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:38.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要不要來試試那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:39.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:43.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是我們在演唱會前唸的咒語
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:47.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不勝惶恐 不勝惶恐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:48.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不會有問題的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:52.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,結丘女子學園偶像社Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:56.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今後也要讓更多更多的人聽見我們的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.42,0:21:57.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小芽衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:21:59.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為我而唱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.21,0:22:01.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為你而唱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:06.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為大家而唱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:12.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我追逐的夢想前方 總是能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:15.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,名為希望的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:20.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,正在閃爍著 閃爍耀眼光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:23.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,即便跌倒也能再次前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:28.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我追逐的夢想前方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:33.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我究竟會走向何處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:38.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,場場相遇之中 雖然又會迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:42.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請試著去享受這一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:45.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,覺得「似乎能做到卻做不到」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:47.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最後做到的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:50.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就會很開心 想著要好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:54.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,整顆心都像是要跳了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:59.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,盡情歡笑 放聲高歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:01.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:05.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,繼續走向遠方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:07.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,世界廣闊無邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然也有景色會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:13.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但熱情會始終如一!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:17.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跨越許多後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:19.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想實現的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:23.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來吧 大家一起去實現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:28.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明天要彈奏出什麼樣的悸動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:32.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去改變未來吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.60,0:23:39.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下集 Money輪流轉
